OL,3,CKey findings: Damming reports from ex-
OL,4,Cborders inspector released
OL,6,FDeputy Political Editor Anushka
OL,7,FAsthana explains following David
OL,8,FNeal's sacking as Chief Inspector of
OL,9,FBorders and Immigrations. Words by
OL,10,FMaya Bowles, ITV Westminster Producer
OL,12,FThe Home Office released 13 reports by
OL,13,Fformer Chief Inspector of Borders and
OL,14,FImmigration, David Neal, on Thursday
OL,15,Fafter he for leaking his reports to
OL,16,Fthe media and putting sensitive
OL,17,Finformation into the public domain.
