OL,6,FMr Neal said the Home Office had been
OL,7,Ftoo slow to publish the papers by his
OL,8,Fdepartment, and that he had been fired
OL,9,Fin a Microsoft Teams call.
OL,11,FThe leaked reports claimed UK Border
OL,12,FForce failed to check hundreds of
OL,13,Fprivate jets arriving at London City
OL,14,Fairport. That report has not yet been
OL,15,Fpublished by the Home Office.
