OL,4,Cborders inspector released
OL,6,FMr Neal's reviews released on Thursday
OL,7,Fare scathing on a number of issues,
OL,8,Fincluding that Home Office data is
OL,9,Foften found to be "poor", that there's
OL,10,Fa "culture of defensiveness", and
OL,11,F"poor communication" by the Home
OL,12,FOffice.
OL,14,FITV News breaks down the most shocking
OL,15,Ffindings from the 13 reports:
OL,17,FBorder Force
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/20
