OL,6,FMr Neal's report on e-passport gates
OL,7,Fat airports found that "the protection
OL,8,Fof the border is neither effective nor
OL,9,Fefficient."
OL,11,FHe said his inspectors observed border
OL,12,Fforce officers "often distracted from
OL,13,Ftheir core operational activity", that
OL,14,Fthere was "a lack of basic
OL,15,Fcommunication equipment", and that
OL,16,F"deployment of resources was
OL,17,Finconsisent".
OL,19,F"This is basic stuff that is not being
OL,20,Fdone well," he wrote.
