OL,6,FAsylum seeker children in hotels
OL,8,FAnother report on conditions from
OL,9,Fasylum seeking children housed in
OL,10,Fhotels said "basic bread-and-butter
OL,11,Fchecks" are not being done - raising
OL,12,Fconcerns around DBS checks on hotel
OL,13,Fstaff.
OL,15,FA report by Mr Neal in 2022 found that
OL,16,Fstaff in two hotels accommodating
OL,17,Fchildren seeking asylum hadn't had DBS
OL,18,Fchecks - Mr Neal said there wasn't
OL,19,Fsufficient assurance this had been
OL,20,Faddressed in his most recent round of
OL,21,Finspections.
