OL,6,FHe noted one hotel in which the staff
OL,7,Fwould "make a game of" telling the
OL,8,Fchildren who would be next to leave
OL,9,Ffor a placement - he says they would
OL,10,Fask children to guess who would be
OL,11,Fnext, before revealing their name.
OL,13,FInspectors considered this to be
OL,14,Finsensitive in the extreme and
OL,15,Fundoubtedly upsetting to the children.
