OL,6,FHe was also critical of the fact that
OL,7,F"more than two months on" from the
OL,8,FHigh Court ruling the systematic
OL,9,Faccommodation of children seeking
OL,10,Fasylum in hotels was unlawful, "the
OL,11,Fhotels were still in use."
OL,13,FMr Neal also said "the Home Office did
OL,14,Fnot have an exit strategy from the use
OL,15,Fof hotels", until legal challenges
OL,16,Fwere brought to challenge it.
