OL,6,FWithdrawn asylum claims
OL,8,FMr Neal also expresses concern about
OL,9,Fthe number of asylum claims being
OL,10,F"withdrawn" by the Home Office.
OL,12,FThe Home Office can withdraw an asylum
OL,13,Fapplication if a claimaint fails to
OL,14,Fmeet certain requirements, like
OL,15,Fmissing an interview or not returning
OL,16,Fa questionnaire in time.
OL,18,FAccording to data released on
OL,19,FThursday, the number of asylum claims
OL,20,Fwithdrawn in 2023 had quadrupled -
OL,21,Ffrom 6,000 in 2022 to 25,600 in 2023.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/20
