OL,6,FMr Neal said the government's "focus
OL,7,Fon clearing the legacy backlog 'at all
OL,8,Fcosts' has led to perverse outcomes
OL,9,Ffor claimants".
OL,11,FThe report said "22 per cent of all
OL,12,Fdecisions made since June 2022 were
OL,13,Fwithdrawals, and, incredible, only one
OL,14,Funderwent formal quality assurance.
OL,15,FThis is not acceptable".
