OL,6,FIn a report on the resettlement of
OL,7,FAfghan refugees, Mr Neal says a lack
OL,8,Fof clear data meant Home Office had to
OL,9,Fresort to "contacting arrivals by
OL,10,Fphone to establish their immigration
OL,11,Fstatus", and that "the Home Office
OL,12,Fgranted permission to stay to British
OL,13,Fcitizens in error".
OL,15,FIn response to Mr Neal's findings, the
OL,16,FHome Office said the following:
