OL,6,F"I think I've been sacked for doing
OL,7,Fwhat the law asks of me and I've
OL,8,Fbreached, I've fallen down over a
OL,9,Fclause in my employment contract,
OL,10,Fwhich I think is a crying shame", Mr
OL,11,FNeal told MPs.
OL,13,FMore than 40 refugee charities
OL,14,Fincluding Freedom from Torture and the
OL,15,FRefugee Council have written to the
OL,16,FHome Secretary with concerns about how
OL,17,FMr Neal's sacking will affect the
OL,18,Fasylum system, saying it "creates a
OL,19,Fvacuum".
