OL,6,FIn an interview with the Daily Mail,
OL,7,FMr Neal claimed the Home Office's
OL,8,Fhandling of his reports was a "scandal
OL,9,Fand incredibly dangerous".
OL,11,FMr Neal's tenure as the independent
OL,12,Fborders watchdog was due to end on
OL,13,FMarch 21 and he claimed No 10 had
OL,14,Fblocked his reappointment before he
OL,15,Fwas ultimately fired.
OL,17,FMigration figures released on Thursday
OL,18,Fshowed and that the government granted
OL,19,Fasylum to 62,336 people - the highest
OL,20,Fnumber since records began.
